Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.13,0:00:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做著夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.54,0:00:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每天所做的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不會結束的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.61,0:00:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.71,0:00:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.68,0:00:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢不會結束的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.99,0:00:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是何時開始的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.46,0:00:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很久很久以前嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.83,0:00:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是前不久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.20,0:00:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也隱藏在夢裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.57,0:00:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不知流逝與否的時間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.41,0:00:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.09,0:01:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時候又到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.66,0:01:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪的季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.63,0:01:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間的黃昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.78,0:02:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行著一段永遠的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.52,0:02:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖繼續探索著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.93,0:02:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片發出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.27,0:02:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.41,0:02:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找遺失的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.62,0:02:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手的掌心確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.02,0:02:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.33,0:02:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間開始流動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好慢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你身上積雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我等了兩個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.88,0:03:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為現在才兩點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.89,0:03:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是兩點也遲到一個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.32,0:03:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是遲到的賠罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.06,0:03:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外順便慶祝我們重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年不見的重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只值一罐咖啡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.87,0:04:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們已經七年不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我的名字嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳還記得我的名字嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.27,0:04:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「雪之少女」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 還沒到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然妳這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們已經走了三個多小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.29,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我們一起撿到小貓的公園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.46,0:05:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小貓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候還有風雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你背吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.34,0:05:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 怎麼能讓女生幫我拿背包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 因為我鍛鍊過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是田徑隊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田徑隊？妳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太大驚小怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他隊員是烏龜跟蝸牛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是一般的正常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 還是我自己拿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睽違一年的北國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.72,0:06:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兒提時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.92,0:06:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我常常來表妹名雪住的這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起到處去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道什麼時候開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有再來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.50,0:06:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺的時光悄悄流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽 我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.47,0:06:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.54,0:06:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面很冷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.08,0:06:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以會突然回到這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.42,0:06:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然調職到國外去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以強迫一個人留在日本的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.19,0:06:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來我表妹名雪家住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那是國外耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想一起去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我連英文都說不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還想說東非話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.54,0:06:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的爸爸調職的地方真不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼事\N盡管告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我們的家人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要打擾妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得名雪跟秋子阿姨都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.56,0:07:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是老實說 我不想回來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7年前來過這裡的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.57,0:07:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得要填滿這段空白\N似乎不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有這個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要哭了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天同一時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在車站前面的椅子上等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還穿著睡衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽 我的制服呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.43,0:08:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快遲到了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.59,0:08:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是會冷的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.43,0:08:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 不應該說“啊”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上應該要說早安才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.17,0:09:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吵醒你了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以多睡一會兒的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是寄人籬下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總不能一直睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在放寒假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺也沒關係呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要出門了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有社團活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我是社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 妳昨天好像有說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概幾點結束？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說社團活動嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天只有開會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概中午過了就能回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我等妳回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以帶我去街上走走嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.27,0:09:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我可以的話當然沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.61,0:09:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為以後你要一直住在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道是不是一直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知道我爸什麼時候回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.12,0:09:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也不能老是住在妳家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.19,0:10:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 妳不會遲到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一百公尺跑七秒就來得及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是世界紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你要吃早飯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.88,0:10:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.78,0:10:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要早一點起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.15,0:10:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子餓扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳來不及了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.09,0:10:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她能早點起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就輕鬆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.22,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪早上都爬不起來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明天開始也要辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 秋子阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.93,0:10:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這好像不是名雪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要若無其事的\N說這麼可怕的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是名雪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.62,0:11:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我從家裡帶來的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得有放進箱子裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 我要去買午飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡吃什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 反正我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且名雪差不多要回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去接了她之後再去買吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,採買中止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不快點去買東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太陽就要下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你說過你會陪我去吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太冷了 我不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以食言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然要吞下一千根針哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就跟我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.19,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 一定不會冷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.46,0:12:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.99,0:12:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.93,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 記得當時我氣呼呼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是很冷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有 今天是晴天所以很溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪跟妳媽媽騙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有騙你 真的不冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳才應該吞下一千根針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是超大根的針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能要吞得下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.66,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有氣勢就可以吞下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.92,0:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.56,0:12:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那你今天的晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有紅生薑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯碗裡滿滿的紅生薑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配紅生薑吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝的東西也只有紅生薑湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼快 店也不會逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會逃走但是會關起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.78,0:13:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我跟名雪\N一起去買晚餐的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是先回去我會生氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們說好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來接妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是騙妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來買午飯的材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨叫我買我喜歡吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我白高興一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 後面的就交給妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.63,0:13:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不是這裡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼東西好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我在這裡等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.54,0:14:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以自己先回去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟當時一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.89,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.08,0:14:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份 我明明叫你讓開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞到人就不過份嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我停不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫妳在雪地上跑步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站得起來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在追我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的我就不能多說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想牽連無辜的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.92,0:15:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經被牽連了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 待會再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 快擋起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他在追妳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.75,0:15:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼看他\N都只是個善良的老爹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能以貌取人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.76,0:16:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個老爹為什麼穿著圍裙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是鯛魚燒的老板吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼鯛魚燒的老板要追妳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.77,0:16:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳從剛才就小心翼翼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱在懷裡的這個紙袋是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我碰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡的鯛魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我買的時候都還很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.99,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要付錢時才發現沒錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.69,0:16:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才拔腿就跑了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.13,0:16:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣聽來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.96,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎全部都是妳單方面的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地方沒辦法了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說來話長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.64,0:16:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是非常錯綜復雜的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳放心 我有的是時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.08,0:17:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是妳不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯛魚燒果然是剛烤好的最好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是有乖乖付錢的人\N才能說的話吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也吃吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.04,0:17:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.01,0:17:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把事情說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向剛才的老爹好好的道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱怨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有錢的話我都嘛有付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.26,0:17:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是亞由 月宮亞由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是祐一 相澤祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.44,0:18:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.74,0:18:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.78,0:18:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能見面就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會見面就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.23,0:18:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.58,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.98,0:18:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.22,0:18:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.30,0:19:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我昨天也遲到了 扯平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們來吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經過了中午
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.81,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.58,0:19:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也真是轟轟烈烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.86,0:19:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 可以去洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.57,0:19:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的鬧鐘可以借我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡哪一個我都可以借你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡收集鬧鐘嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 哪一個好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就暫時借用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.04,0:20:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要說晚安哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.08,0:20:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.32,0:20:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是相澤祐一 妳呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是亞由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由？？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姓什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.70,0:20:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由亞由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.21,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.68,0:21:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.92,0:21:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我去買點東西來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.76,0:21:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.46,0:21:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯛魚燒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛烤好的鯛魚燒最棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.87,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好鹹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是眼淚的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.78,0:21:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.02,0:21:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想吃鯛魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.53,0:21:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們下次再一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.34,0:21:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天同一時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.71,0:21:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在車站前面的椅子上等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.64,0:21:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.65,0:22:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.72,0:22:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勾勾手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.85,0:22:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用勾手我也一定會來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.02,0:22:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勾勾手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.83,0:22:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.70,0:22:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在乳白色的晨曦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.30,0:22:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打了個瞌睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.77,0:22:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是作夢還是回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.98,0:22:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個答案就連在夢裡也很朦朧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.61,0:22:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上了 早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.88,0:22:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快吃早飯 去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.53,0:23:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從隨風飄流的雲朵之間\N窺視到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.31,0:23:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連熟悉的街道也閃閃發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.85,0:23:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.03,0:23:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.93,0:23:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真來蓋過溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.58,0:23:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間靜悄悄的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.28,0:23:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂著溫柔的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.86,0:24:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為凍僵的思念也會化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.27,0:24:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始念同一所學校的表兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.47,0:24:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及他們的朋友們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.21,0:24:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的體內靜止的時光的指針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.24,0:24:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又開始轉動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.61,0:24:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanon第2話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.15,0:24:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽光和昫的街道
